+## 7) Detección de IA — `POST /api/v1/search/ai-detection`
+
+```bash
+curl -X POST $BASE/api/v1/search/ai-detection \
+  -H "X-API-Key: $API_KEY" -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
+  -d '{"image_url":"https://ejemplo.com/foto.jpg"}'
+```
+```python
+r = requests.post(f"{BASE}/api/v1/search/ai-detection", headers=HEADERS,
