+## 10) Admin (requiere `X-Admin-Key`) y Jobs
+
+```bash
+# Listar items (lectura, X-API-Key)
+curl -H "X-API-Key: $API_KEY" "$BASE/api/v1/admin/collection/items?limit=100&group_id=proyecto_x"
+curl -H "X-API-Key: $API_KEY" $BASE/api/v1/admin/models
+
+# Borrar grupo (destructivo → X-Admin-Key)
+curl -X DELETE -H "X-Admin-Key: $ADMIN_KEY" $BASE/api/v1/admin/collection/groups/proyecto_x
+
+# Reset total (destructivo → X-Admin-Key + token de confirmación)
+curl -X DELETE $BASE/api/v1/admin/collection/reset \
+  -H "X-Admin-Key: $ADMIN_KEY" -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
+  -d '{"confirm":"I_UNDERSTAND_THIS_WILL_DELETE_ALL_DATA"}'
+
+# Estado de job async
+curl -H "X-API-Key: $API_KEY" $BASE/api/v1/jobs/<job_id>
+```
+```python
+requests.get(f"{BASE}/api/v1/admin/collection/items",
+             headers=HEADERS, params={"limit": 100, "group_id": "proyecto_x"})
+requests.delete(f"{BASE}/api/v1/admin/collection/reset", headers=ADMIN,
+                json={"confirm": "I_UNDERSTAND_THIS_WILL_DELETE_ALL_DATA"})
+requests.get(f"{BASE}/api/v1/jobs/{job_id}", headers=HEADERS)   # poll hasta status=done
+```
